I"V<p>A base URL to use <em>instead</em> of the one set in the <a href="/integrations/http/">http component</a>. It is used as-is by the <code>tts</code> component. In particular, you need to include the protocol scheme <code>http://</code> or <code>https://</code> and the correct port number. They will not be automatically added for you.</p>
